      "text": "While the Cartesian mindset, based on intellectual rationalism, birthed by the Enlightenment and become the dominant worldview, we would be amiss if we did not name two others ways of knowing that are powerful and valuable in their own right, what we could call Eastern Ways of Knowing and [[Indigenous Ways of Knowing]]. "
    },
